&lt;p&gt;This message is automatically generated.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12933663" author="eli" created="Fri, 19 Nov 2010 04:00:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t see any additional javadoc warnings with this patch (same # warnings are reported before and after applying this patch).   I&apos;ve committed this.  Thanks Sanjay!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
